# Deployment Workflow

Before any push to GitHub or deployment to Vercel:

1. Run `npm run build` locally — must pass with zero errors
2. Run `npm run lint` — fix errors, review warnings
3. Verify `.env.local` has no empty required variables
4. Verify `company-config.json` has no empty required fields
5. Remove stray `console.log` statements from `src/`
6. Commit with conventional commit format: `type(scope): description`

Types: feat, fix, style, refactor, docs, chore, perf, test
